title: #137 - Sean Conroy & ME
description: Comedian, Actor, & Podcaster Sean Conroy and I hang out in the Mancave and talk about looking like big aggressive men, Micro-agressions, stand-up, Improv, the UCB, and him beating me out for the co-hosting job of Nevermind the Buzzcocks.
